{"tid":601393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7支那人被騙走600萬 闖尖沙咀倫敦金公司爆樽架頸","createTime":"2018-03-22T07:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T10:25:24.000Z","uid":39539,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e738718622b12a2ae498fcafe41e847e95fc5ca2","tid":601393,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:44:44.000Z","msg":"中午12時40分，4男3女走到尖沙嘴新港中心1座6樓一間投資公司，與職員爭執。其間有人打爛玻璃樽架頸要脅，職員連忙報警求助。警員接報到場游說，並找來談判專家協助。<br />\n資料顯示，本月7日，6名手持玻璃樽的內地人，同樣走到上址投資公司，要求與公司職員理論。據稱，6人來自不同省份，他們從微信收到訊息，投資逾600萬元於股票、倫敦金等，但全數蝕錢。爭執期間有人打爆玻璃樽，揚言要傷害自己，職員報警。雙方對峙4小時，男子放下玻璃樽，經勸喻後離去。"},{"pid":"eeabc3c89faea9b917933140e4f1c0cfbbd3952c","tid":601393,"uid":168506,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:46:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ddaad0e28c06dd52c59828ffc6a5aba52a3e2a5","tid":601393,"uid":653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5ff597ecf59675e5a0ab5eb9a71167f3720ee6","tid":601393,"uid":36502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"點解要傷害自己....."},{"pid":"3fb507d5f4bce34ce979e055c0e499989da88c86","tid":601393,"uid":84228,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:49:36.000Z","msg":"唔知要幫邊個好，唯有食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f4fd1a9ecc2d31ed23e0b1261d567c02a08f94","tid":601393,"uid":3241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:49:55.000Z","msg":"點解爆左樽黑警都可以放佢走，<br />\n換轉香港人一定要返警署行返轉嫁喎"},{"pid":"77963871ac36ab3a348e239197df09f35ba73c84","tid":601393,"uid":39539,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/154838_09ce3bbbae9601bf7476